item.description: Cecilia Dapino is an undergraduate student at Case Western Reserve University (CWRU) in Cleveland, Ohio. She is set to receive her B.S. in Biology and Statistics in spring 2026. Ceci worked as a 2025 Summer Student Fellow in the Alexander Lab, working on identifying and classifying Gephyrocapsa huxleyi viruses with genomic data and bioinformatics computer software. Now, as a guest student, she will be continuing this research in pursuit of her senior capstone at CWRU.
